---
title: BBQ Prawn & Slaw Tacos with Cheddar Cheese & Plant-Based Mayo
description: It’s a good day when you’re having tacos for dinner. Let’s pack these tortillas with as much All-American spiced prawns as possible, topped with a colourful slaw and avocado. Don’t forget the Cheddar cheese for the perfect finishing touch!
